  them at the workshop and only carry tiny moving parts, like doors and
  buttons, to your play table. Websites can work the same way. This guide
  helps you do heavy work on the server and send only the fun interactive
  pieces to people using the app. It also teaches your app to remember
  answers it already found so it does less repeated work and feels faster.

